    <item>
      <title>借助热门通胀数据，财富管理机构为投资者带来了第二次机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/investment-opportunities-with-hot-inflation-higher-for-longer-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[不断上涨的价格和高利率令投资者感到沮丧。但顾问表示，顽固的价格增长为潜在利润丰厚的举措赢得了时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/investment-opportunities-with-hot-inflation-higher-for-longer-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 13:07:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>钢铁自由贸易并不存在：Tai</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-19/there-s-no-such-thing-as-free-trade-in-steel-tai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国贸易代表凯瑟琳·泰表示，美国正试图阻止钢铁进入墨西哥，然后以墨西哥钢铁的名义不正当地进入美国。她在“彭博监视”节目中发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-19/there-s-no-such-thing-as-free-trade-in-steel-tai</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 13:04:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港监管机构将调查普华永道对恒大的审计角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/hong-kong-regulator-to-probe-pwc-auditing-role-over-evergrande</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港会计监管机构表示，在接到“举报”后，将调查有关普华永道会计师事务所审计中国恒大集团的指控。]]></description>
